txt.en: '[placeholder], your help is needed in Eshadûr. We have received word that the Ordâkhai captured several people and took them to their stronghold. A witness reports seeing Dokhára with them. He is greatly feared by the Ambarûli and is known for torturing his prisoners. Quickly, you must get to Eshadûr and rescue these people!'
You have freed the prisoners in Eshadûr and defeated Dokhára! Return with Khâdamul to report your success.
There is no twist in this mission.
The Ordâkhai torturer Dokhára is holding several Ambarûli people prisoner in Eshadûr.
'Thank you for rescuing the prisoners in Eshadûr. It is a relief that Dokhára did not get much time with them.'
'Your mission is to rescue the prisoners being held in Eshadûr and save them from the Ordâkhai torturer Dokhára.'
Complete Mission: In Need of Rescue
Your mission is to rescue the prisoners being held in Eshadûr and save them from the Ordâkhai torturer Dokhára.\n\nTalk to Khâdamul when you are ready to get underway.
